%section#HowToConnect
  :markdown
    ## How To Connect

    You plug in the "Grove Speaker" by connecting the Grove cable to the speaker, and then plugging the other end of the cable to whichever digital port you wish to use on your Grove shield. For example, `D4`.

        :::javascript
        Cylon.robot({
          connections: {
            edison: { adaptor: "intel-iot" }
          },

          devices: {
            speaker: {
              driver: "upm-grovespeaker",
              pin: 4
            }
          },
        ...

%section#HowToUse
  :markdown
    ## How To Use

    Example using the UPM Grove Speaker driver:

        :::javascript
        var Cylon = require("cylon");

        Cylon.robot({
          connections: {
            edison: { adaptor: "intel-iot" }
          },

          devices: {
            speaker: {
              driver: "upm-grovespeaker",
              pin: 4
            }
          },

          work: function(my) {
            my.speaker.playSound("a", true, "low");
            my.speaker.playSound("c", true, "low");
            my.speaker.playSound("d", true, "low");
            my.speaker.playSound("b", false, "low");
          }

        }).start();


