      # Commands

      ## playSound(char letter, bool sharp, string vocalWeight)

      Play back a sound using the speaker. For example: `speaker.playSound("c", true, "med");` will play back a C-sharp note in the medium register.

      ## playAll()

      Play all 7 of the lowest notes.

